Package org.lsmp.djep.matrixJep Description

Advanced vector and matrix handeling. For a simplier and smaller vector and matrix handeling see vectorJep. This package adds:

  • ability to differentiate equations with vectors and matricies
  • overloaded ^ operator which can be either cross product or power
  • slightly faster evaluation
Sub-packages
